										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p>During the AAPT Winter Meeting in St. Louis, Missouri, the open-access book <a href="https://interactivetextbooks.tudelft.nl/showthephysics" data-type="link" data-id="https://interactivetextbooks.tudelft.nl/showthephysics">Show the Physics</a> has been presented. This book has been made using the Teachbook tool. Attendees were pointed to Teachbooks as a tool to (re)create and (re)use educational content.</p>



