										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p>We provided an in-house training with <a href="https://www.onderwijsnetwerkzuidholland.nl/" data-type="link" data-id="https://www.onderwijsnetwerkzuidholland.nl/">Betasteunpunt Zuid Holland</a>. In this four hour training session, we introduced 29 participants &#8211; ranging from secondary school teachers to associate professors, and from teacher educators to retired medical doctors &#8211; to the basics of Jupyter Books.</p>



